		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The ideal future goal is synthesis onto an FPGA or eventually an ASIC from a definition written in an HDL to perform a potentially perfect recreation of the system. This also makes compatibility with old hardware not hard at all, and you remove a lot of layers that introduce delays in both the input and output from the whole setup.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


